data.text: @wmag @khloekardashian True is blessed to have you for a mom. You are the most genuine, kind, honest, loving, hardworking beautiful soul I’ve have see in a long time. You always be you and the world will adjusts❤️😘

@wmag @khloekardashian you are a true inspiration to so many. I have two kids and what you had to go thru on national tv yet put your feelings aside to have True have her dad present and that she always knows that she is loved is more then so many would be able to do!!
